{"tid":1264913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃繼兒：以恐嚇性目的使用個人資料屬於違法(商台新聞)","createTime":"2019-06-29T02:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T03:36:49.000Z","uid":156254,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"007bd7422f499ed0614fecbd21a333ba37463c0f","tid":1264913,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:34:14.000Z","msg":"黃繼兒：以恐嚇性目的使用個人資料屬於違法(商台新聞)<br />\n私隱專員黃繼兒指，公署收到約200宗涉及警員正式投訴，主要指警員的個人資料和圖片被放上網，當中抵毀、侮辱或恐嚇說話令他們或他們的家庭成員受驚，投訴數字不斷增加。他指，公署有主動接觸網站、社交平台和討論區營運商，勸喻他們移除侵犯個人資料的內容，如果屢勸不改，甚至可以刪除帳戶，營運商都會從善如流遵從指引。<br />\n<br />\n黃繼兒在本台節目指，近日關於醫院披露個人資料投訴個案有36宗，正作循規審查。他指出，醫護人員對病人私隱有非常嚴格保護，需要強而有力証據，令醫護人員由保護個人資料轉為披露，例如如果不使用這些資料，會影響罪案偵察和拘捕，就屬於例外情況。他指，在醫護人員的專業守則亦有提及，如何平衡利益和損害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433ff205061ceb2d132353495cf101fa460e7790","tid":1264913,"uid":28878,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"邊條法例？"},{"pid":"8c5f2352f273f45c9a28b4b1b182ed08bcd5e20d","tid":1264913,"uid":66055,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"繼兒動母"},{"pid":"5e8dc4df4f03ad8fd0e8841883b552761e7840d3","tid":1264913,"uid":264965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:42:16.000Z","msg":"表揚姐"},{"pid":"45d328ac8df37c77843fc5382cfbc20c1ff79951","tid":1264913,"uid":85629,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:44:51.000Z","msg":"兩句總結：黑警用任何方法拎市民資料合法；市民發放黑警自己公開既個人資料就錯"},{"pid":"a424841bb86ac3692a5e804985da9604725efe6e","tid":1264913,"uid":93932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:52:57.000Z","msg":"要繼續做"},{"pid":"6b06dafe783953dfb59fff2080c764869b133e03","tid":1264913,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:53:54.000Z","msg":"表揚得唔得先<br />\n我覺得香港差佬好型好有江湖味喎"},{"pid":"8a23e620b8e18524dda88cf5887a4a82c6f3b50b","tid":1264913,"uid":155374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋只係間接承認咗邊啲人做得唔啱，要保護佢哋唔俾人公開<br />\n<br />\n做得啱，放出嚟表揚，冇人會嘈；<br />\n做得唔啱，放出嚟就係侵犯私隱<br />\n<br />\n方向錯咗，應該係要教下冇接受過高等教育嘅警員點樣處理個人資料，唔好自己放晒上網公開晒"},{"pid":"54942ed619680043c48d59b2d75c5cec4001f1a9","tid":1264913,"uid":34383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"犯法你咪拉人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55bf970252885d7466b383c7984ef7c84fc1e1d","tid":1264913,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:08:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7ffe11434ba52d92bf0130dda8ed2e64e6aaad28","tid":1264913,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:12:35.000Z","msg":"表揚香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a006a2e4e5335a1bc43a2fdb93531d5d2616d22","tid":1264913,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:13:32.000Z","msg":"繼兒動母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9bc8a1c5856b2b733eaa6a961cf9d733e049d2","tid":1264913,"uid":77092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:15:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da4d0de63e3038f4dfbb8c353eeaca8bd2e8cc06","tid":1264913,"uid":77092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:17:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1fd19eef3842813e092d5652878ae6b1791cabee","tid":1264913,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:18:33.000Z","msg":"繼續吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23474297afe6834a7353f4daf93ad3f8c62a6c7","tid":1264913,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:20:39.000Z","msg":"首先放喺公開平台（eg:Facebook) 仲係個人資料咩？"},{"pid":"37b62e943d1397ba625cf401daaf149e5006f137","tid":1264913,"uid":42149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:35:16.000Z","msg":"放得上social media 就等於願意公開自己資訊上internet<br />\n<br />\n轉貼都犯法，on撚鳩"},{"pid":"1742cb20cb2a7e946854aeb8f886ce700574448d","tid":1264913,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"純公開就冇事？"}]}